{"tid":2335580,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 滷肉鐵路便當","createTime":"2020-12-22T04:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T07:54:27.000Z","uid":33359,"like":182,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3566f3238610e8cb88da4e817ea94cd3385094","tid":2335580,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b0mcr9h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0mcr9h.jpg&h=339f178e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/59bLM9j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F59bLM9j.jpg&h=4ae14693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyjhDf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyjhDf0.jpg&h=3f8e5c74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n滷肉係我最鍾意個隻連皮滷肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬肉切成丁狀再去滷製<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個油脂香氣重好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肥肉位甘香,瘦肉位有咬口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n滷汁都非常入味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小菜方面除咗椰菜有少少草青味之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他都好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢個飯真係煲得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好煙UN<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能因為係佢用木製飯盒,D倒汗水完全無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我拎返公司隔咗都差唔多10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成盒飯都係無俾倒汗水搞到水汪汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得連肥佬黎先生都讚話離開台灣之外未食過咁好食既滷肉飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c-znEsGUe9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc-znEsGUe9E&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FbhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=515fb5be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c-znEsGUe9E</a><br />\n<br />\n食落個椎間盤突出位好C伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a07ffb97e88d5ec7aeef349fe021ca7d59b7a2","tid":2335580,"uid":367007,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:07:02.000Z","msg":"鐵路師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207c4a8bb41cefa7aa4551349feeb6227afb6add","tid":2335580,"uid":43785,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"邊度？"},{"pid":"bee2b0d1e43356db7a947e52d7c24d2f9a0d1ec1","tid":2335580,"uid":317749,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:07:08.000Z","msg":"滷肉師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1d76bd59fe340ff3fa5d67a421a772a834802d","tid":2335580,"uid":317749,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"207c4a8bb41cefa7aa4551349feeb6227afb6add","tid":2335580,"uid":43785,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"邊度？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:07:23.000Z","msg":"你點邊度的？"},{"pid":"2783e3dd722f047138af13ace2cdcba35f5611ce","tid":2335580,"uid":33359,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"207c4a8bb41cefa7aa4551349feeb6227afb6add","tid":2335580,"uid":43785,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"邊度？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"你點邊的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4229ec6af6ce7716deb