yTime":"2020-12-22T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b0mcr9h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0mcr9h.jpg&h=339f178e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/59bLM9j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F59bLM9j.jpg&h=4ae14693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyjhDf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyjhDf0.jpg&h=3f8e5c74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n滷肉係我最鍾意個隻連皮滷肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬肉切成丁狀再去滷製<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個油脂香氣重好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肥肉位甘香,瘦肉位有咬口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n滷汁都非常入味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小菜方面除咗椰菜有少少草青味之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他都好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢個飯真係煲得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好煙UN<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能因為係佢用木製飯盒,D倒汗水完全無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我拎返公司隔咗都差唔多10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成盒飯都係無俾倒汗水搞到水汪汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得連肥佬黎先生都讚話離開台灣之外未食過咁好食既滷肉飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c-znEsGUe9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc-znEsGUe9E&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FbhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=515fb5be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c-znEsGUe9E</a><br />\n<br />\n食落個椎間盤突出位好C伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:18:50.000Z","msg":"椎姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339bf291e5d678ad09a84fbd94904bb8a8e1f165","tid":2335580,"uid":302668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:19:57.000Z","msg":"定廷火車便當<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4893900e8222effe145262d4a42faa765839949","tid":2335580,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"90c0251cea5f05f64fb9d6843f20f7eb66c4c24b","tid":2335580,"uid":97028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:01:12.000Z","msg":"觀塘？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"你點知的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5a73ef6f2b76b18bc63e0f38548d8c124c29e8","tid":2335580,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:26:09.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎 ： 好正 好正 / 唔該 唔該 / 好正 好正<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929d1f8e8dc88783b2fe91ce7747f733a675767d","tid":2335580,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"呢間野一年前食D店員串到仆街,唔識招呼同安排"},{"pid":"1e5d45f752c5a92fc20246e96c990c6a97aea8bc","tid":2335580,"uid":129946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"總舖師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5098f3d6724b26983650c247fad497e148f4862d","tid":2335580,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quot